\begin_layout Solution
1) Пусть 
\begin_inset Formula $x,y\in K\left(G\right)$
\end_inset

.
 Тогда 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 и 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

