\begin_inset Formula $\varphi$
\end_inset

 — гомоморфизм, то 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi\left(g_{1}\right)\varphi\left(g_{2}\right)=\varphi\left(g_{1}g_{2}\right)$
\end_inset

 
