\begin_inset Formula $\varphi\left(\left(x_{1},y_{1}\right)\left(x_{2},y_{2}\right)\right)=\varphi\left(\left(x_{1}x_{2},y_{1}y_{2}\right)\right)=\left(\left(x_{1}x_{2}\right)N_{1},\left(y_{1}y_{2}\right)N_{2}\right)$
\end_inset

.
