=\left(\left(a_{1}+a_{2}\right)a_{3}-\left(b_{1}+b_{2}\right)b_{3},\left(a_{1}+a_{2}\right)b_{3}+\left(b_{1}+b_{2}\right)a_{3}\right)=\\
