, то 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|z\right|=\sqrt{1+3}=2$
\end_inset

 (по формуле 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "prob:absolute-value-of-complex-number-formula"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) и 
\begin_inset Formula $\cos\varphi=-\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\sin\varphi=\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}$
\end_inset

.
 Можно взять 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi=\frac{2\pi}{3}$
\end_inset

, тогда 
\begin_inset Formula $z=-1+i\sqrt{3}=2\left(\cos\frac{2\pi}{3}+i\sin\frac{2\pi}{3}\right)$
